{"tid":1539423,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【核彈】審視主權！９月８日美領！[bomb]reviewHKSovereignty!demoToUSConsulate","createTime":"2019-09-04T09:54:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T17:23:49.000Z","uid":87858,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"2e88b3d37f6e2435a6f3f43293f51093bf3a15af","tid":1539423,"uid":87858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:54:11.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【審視主權，港人自決！】<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EVdYMNX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEVdYMNX.jpg&h=eabbcdc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nREVIEW HK SOVEREIGNTY NOW<br />\nOUR OWN FATE IN OUR HANDS</span></strong></span><br />\n</div><br />\n(see english below)<br />\n大家比林奠撤回搶哂討論焦點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上得黎都知五大訴求缺一不可啦<br />\n而家唔可以剩係等土共施捨比我地<br />\n<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>我地仲有好多條戰線架！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n距離<span style=\"color: red;\">美國復會</span>仲有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">８日</span></strong></span><br />\n９月８日美領遊行！<br />\n要求盡快通過<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>香港民主及人權法</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/D4W0eZF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD4W0eZF.jpg&h=31b6d7fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>香港主權爭議</strong></span></span><br />\n共產黨<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>違反左中英聯合聲明</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hfptpzV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhfptpzV.jpg&h=2e10b653&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nCarrie Lam's withdrawal is taking all the spot light at this moment lah <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nwtf are you guys doing ah!!????<br />\nAND we CANNOT WAIT for the PRC to give us what we want <br />\nWe have <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">FIGHT FOR IT OURSELVES</span></strong><br />\nThere is still<span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong> SO MUCH LEFT TO DO</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nThere is<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong> 8 DAYS</strong></span> until the resume of the US congress meeting<br />\nwe need to ask them to pass the<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">[ Hong Kong Human Rights and Democracy Act ]</span></span></strong><br />\nAS SOON AS POSSIBLE<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/sKoFeYN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsKoFeYN.jpg&h=8cf36f04&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nthere is also the <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>CONTROVERSY on HK's SOVEREIGNTY!!!!</strong></span></span><br />\nThe PRC has<span style=\"color: gold;\"> violate the SINO-BRITISH Joint Declaration</span><br />\nand no one is talking about it!??<br />\n<br />\nseiously!?? Linden Jai?? TIME TO DO SOME REAL STUFF!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[center]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【審視主權，港人自決！】<br />\nREVIEW HK SOVEREIGNTY NOW<br />\nOUR OWN FATE IN OUR HANDS</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"7540f4a9ebe0a98295653aaf0d5b7270f78985aa","tid":1539423,"uid