關門 而當時有其他性別既警員在場<br />\n-有日本人被捕 警方拒絕比佢聯繫大使館<br />\n-目擊者話傷者係送去瑪嘉烈唔係廣華<br />\n-速龍落電梯 踩住市民背部甚至頭部落<br />\n-去晒葵涌警署有70人（當中有啲係港島拘捕）<br />\n-凌晨時分有部分被拘捕人士送上全黑車往新屋嶺<br />\n-被捕人士名單有備注（例如：知名社工）"},{"pid":"756245a2c69cfd704d1724e8b7a689da5c769eec","tid":1539423,"uid":87858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:00:51.000Z","msg":"10/10"},{"pid":"d148a651b72e51c61ed5bcf61c8f0e16e124707b","tid":1539423,"uid":80560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"香港陷入人道危機,請求美國支援"},{"pid":"85d9d12b3874d5c9f25d6c108bf8b7e0a945fc4c","tid":1539423,"uid":87858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:01:03.000Z","msg":"11/10"},{"pid":"e8be60557eb91e3fe123a6a92137f08ad8ae81d9","tid":1539423,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:01:13.000Z","msg":"你地係咪仲天真以為呢個政府值得我地信任？仲信政府既承諾？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538706\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538706</a><br />\n要記住，香港唔係一個地方，係住呢度既人！我地先係香港既核心，香港既主人！無左我地，政府根本唔係一回事！點解要比依個草菅人命既政府拖住鼻子走！<br />\n有人以為宣告一國兩制同中英聯合聲明失效就會無西方國家幫手，其實唔啱<br />\n只要你將呢場運動變成自由民主vs極權主義<br />\n外國係無得唔幫。9月8日，不見不散！"},{"pid":"7aee3641b1595db4a017358c6ce53d24cb713fc3","tid":1539423,"uid":300641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:01:25.000Z","msg":"要去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0899466d914052ef881b8a33181d87307390411a","tid":1539423,"uid":23407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:01:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbtw<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">The Hong Kong Policy Act, authored by Sen. Mitch McConnell (R-Ky.) and enacted in 1992, allows the president to apply to Hong Kong those laws that address the People&rsquo;s Republic of China. The law&rsquo;s power is selective and flexible, however, and not necessarily all-or-nothing for Hong Kong&rsquo;s special status. For example, the Tiananmen sanctions could be applied to target the city&rsquo;s police force, which has collaborated with organized crime, instigated violence and now might be torturing detained demonstrators.</code></pre><br />\n<a href=\"https://beta.washingtonpost.com/opinions/global-opinions/marco-rubio-china-must-respect-hong-kongs-autonomy--or-face-the-consequences/2019/09/03/7399e69a-ce80-11e9-b29b-a528dc82154a_story.html?noredirect=on\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbeta.washingtonpost.com%2Fopinions%2Fglobal-opinions%2Fmarco-rubio-china-must-respect-hong-kongs-autonomy--or-face-the-consequences%2F2019%2F09%2F03%2F7399e69a-ce80-11e9-b29b-a528dc82154a_story.html%3Fnoredirect%3Don&d=vI%2FQCok0BRDS6jHm%2BKkcajKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=e11a5777\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://beta.washingtonpost.com/opinions/global-opinions/marco-rubio-china-must-respect-hong-kongs-autonomy--or-face-the-consequences/2019/09/03/7399e69a-ce80-11e9-b29b-a528dc82154a_story.html?noredirect=on</a> <br />\n係咪姐係包埋黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f59d21e71faae63c3923608fa15a4960fe2fc6","tid":1539423,"uid":268725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:01:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8B39Niu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8B39Niu.png&h=c9eeccd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce7d2ce078956c5475ef638c2209e57741600edc","tid":1539423,"uid":87858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,